Dialogue: 0,1:40:42.39,1:40:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请打开主舱门  哈尔\NOpen the pod-bay doors, please, Hal.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:52.61,1:40:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请打开主舱门  哈尔\NOpen the pod-bay doors, please, Hal.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:00.37,1:41:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈尔  能听到我说话吗\NHello, Hal, do you read me?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.62,1:41:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈尔  能听到我说话吗\NHello, Hal, do you read me?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:08.46,1:41:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听到了吗  哈尔\NDo you read me, Hal?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.38,1:41:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听到了吗  哈尔\NDo you read me, Hal?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.38,1:41:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈尔  能听到我说话吗\NHello, Hal, do you read me?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.35,1:41:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈尔  能听到我说话吗\NHello, Hal, do you read me?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:23.72,1:41:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听到了吗  哈尔\NDo you read me, Hal?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.52,1:41:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  大卫  我听到了\NAffirmative, Dave. I read you.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:31.52,1:41:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打开主舱门  哈尔\NOpen the pod-bay doors, Hal.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:34.90,1:41:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  大卫  恐怕我做不到\NI'm sorry, Dave. I'm afraid I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:40.99,1:41:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出什么问题了\NWhat's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:43.03,1:41:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你和我一样清楚问题在哪里\NI think you know what the problem is just as well as I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.54,1:41:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么  哈尔\NWhat are you talking about, Hal?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.37,1:41:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这项任务对我至关重要\NThis mission is too important for me
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.42,1:41:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我绝不允许你破坏\Nto allow you to jeopardize it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:54.71,1:41:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你在说什么  哈尔\NI don't know what you're talking about, Hal.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:58.92,1:42:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你和弗兰克打算断开我的连接\NI know that you and Frank were planning to disconnect me...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:03.26,1:42:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕我不能允许这种事发生\Nand I'm afraid that's something I cannot allow to happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.23,1:42:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会这么想  哈尔\NWhere did you get that idea, Hal?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.61,1:42:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大卫  虽然你们在舱内极力防范我...\NDave, although you took very thorough precautions in the pod...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.03,1:42:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听见你们说话\Nagainst my hearing you...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:20.65,1:42:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我能看懂你们的唇语\NI could see your lips move.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:34.96,1:42:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  哈尔\NAll right, Hal.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:39.80,1:42:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从紧急气闸舱进去\NI'll go in through the emergency air lock.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:44.14,1:42:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没有头盔  大卫\NWithout your space helmet, Dave...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.31,1:42:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很难做到\Nyou're going to find that rather difficult.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:50.81,1:42:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈尔  我不跟你争辩了\NHal, I won't argue with you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.15,1:42:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打开舱门\NOpen the doors.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:55.02,1:42:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大卫\NDave...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.73,1:43:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们之间的对话没有意义了  再见\Nthis conversation can serve no purpose anymore. Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.57,1:43:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈尔\NHal?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:05.99,1:43:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈尔\NHal?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:09.75,1:43:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈尔\NHal?
