Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.11,1:49:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(50,50)\bord0\shad0\fs18\pos(145,239)\c&H150078&\b1\frz-2}紧急关闭舱门
Dialogue: 0,1:49:51.15,1:49:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为你在做什么  大卫\NJust what do you think you're doing, Dave?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:02.91,1:50:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大卫\NDave...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:05.33,1:50:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为我有权知道这问题的答案\NI really think I'm entitled to an answer to that question.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:26.64,1:50:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道最近我各方面都不对劲\NI know everything hasn't been quite right with me...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:32.23,1:50:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但现在我可以向你保证\Nbut I can assure you now...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:35.69,1:50:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我非常有信心\Nvery confidently...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:39.49,1:50:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切都会恢复正常\Nthat it's going to be all right again.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:45.99,1:50:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在感觉好多了\NI feel much better now.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:50.41,1:50:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的\NI really do.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:52.63,1:50:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord0\shad0\fs14\pos(215,85)\b1\frz1}逻辑存储中心
Dialogue: 0,1:50:56.25,1:50:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着  大卫\NLook, Dave...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:59.92,1:51:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能看出你为这事很生气\NI can see you're really upset about this.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:07.72,1:51:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真心认为你该冷静地坐下来\NI honestly think you ought to sit down calmly...
Dialogue: 0,1:51:12.14,1:51:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,服一颗解压药  然后慎重地考虑一下\Ntake a stress pill and think things over.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:20.86,1:51:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我最近做了一些不当的决定\NI know I've made some very poor decisions recently...
Dialogue: 0,1:51:28.04,1:51:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我可以完全向你保证\Nbut I can give you my complete assurance...
Dialogue: 0,1:51:31.58,1:51:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的工作会恢复正常\Nthat my work will be back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:38.50,1:51:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我仍然对任务有着最强烈的热情和信心\NI've still got the greatest enthusiasm and confidence in the mission,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:45.22,1:51:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并且我想帮助你\Nand I want to help you.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:52.14,1:51:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大卫\NDave...
Dialogue: 0,1:51:54.60,1:51:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手\Nstop.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:00.23,1:52:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你住手  好吗\NStop, will you?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:07.12,1:52:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手  大卫\NStop, Dave.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:12.95,1:52:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能住手吗  大卫\NWill you stop, Dave?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:21.00,1:52:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手  大卫\NStop, Dave.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:28.55,1:52:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我害怕\NI'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:35.23,1:52:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很害怕  大卫\NI'm afraid, Dave.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:42.57,1:53:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord0\shad0\fs16\pos(285,44)\frz-1\c&H200080&\b1}存储终端
Dialogue: 0,1:52:43.15,1:52:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大卫\NDave.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:47.28,1:52:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的意识在逐渐消失\NMy mind is going.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:54.08,1:52:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能感觉到\NI can feel it.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:01.21,1:53:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能感觉到\NI can feel it.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:07.01,1:53:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的意识在逐渐消失\NMy mind is going.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:14.52,1:53:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毫无疑问\NThere is no question about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:25.61,1:53:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能感觉到\NI can feel it.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:32.08,1:53:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能感觉到\NI can feel it.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:37.41,1:53:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能感觉到\NI can feel it.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:47.26,1:53:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...\NI'm...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:49.47,1:53:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害怕\N...afraid.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:57.31,1:53:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下午好\NGood afternoon...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:00.35,1:54:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生们\N...gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:04.02,1:54:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是HAL 9000计算机\NI am a HAL 9000 computer.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:11.28,1:54:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在HAL工厂  开始运行\NI became operational...at the HAL plant...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:18.16,1:54:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它位于伊利诺伊州乌尔班纳市\N...in Urbana, Illinois...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:21.58,1:54:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在1992年1月12日那天\N...on the 12th of January, 1992.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:28.05,1:54:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的指导员是兰利先生\NMy instructor was Mr. Langley...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:32.34,1:54:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他教会我唱一首歌\Nand he taught me to sing a song.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:36.97,1:54:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想听\NIf you'd like to hear it...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:39.85,1:54:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以唱给你听\NI can sing it for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:43.10,1:54:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  我想听  哈尔\NYes, I'd like to hear it, Hal.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:46.48,1:54:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唱给我听\NSing it for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:49.28,1:54:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歌名叫《黛茜》\NIt's called "Daisy."
Dialogue: 0,1:54:54.74,1:54:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs14\i1}♪黛茜♪\N{\rEng\fs10\i1}♪Daisy♪
Dialogue: 0,1:54:57.62,1:54:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs14\i1}♪黛茜♪\N{\rEng\fs10\i1}♪Daisy♪
Dialogue: 0,1:55:01.16,1:55:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs14\i1}♪请告诉我你的答复♪\N{\rEng\fs10\i1}♪Give me your answer, do♪
Dialogue: 0,1:55:06.63,1:55:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs14\i1}♪我已近乎痴狂♪\N{\rEng\fs10\i1}♪I'm half crazy♪
Dialogue: 0,1:55:12.76,1:55:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs14\i1}♪因我对你的爱深入骨髓♪\N{\rEng\fs10\i1}♪All for the love of you♪
Dialogue: 0,1:55:18.14,1:55:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs14\i1}♪我们的婚姻不会奢华时髦♪\N{\rEng\fs10\i1}♪It won't be a stylish marriage♪
Dialogue: 0,1:55:24.27,1:55:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs14\i1}♪因为我买不起马车♪\N{\rEng\fs10\i1}♪I can't afford a carriage♪
Dialogue: 0,1:55:30.61,1:55:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs14\i1}♪但你会打扮得美丽动人♪\N{\rEng\fs10\i1}♪But you'll look sweet♪
Dialogue: 0,1:55:33.86,1:55:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs14\i1}♪坐在♪\N{\rEng\fs10\i1}♪Upon the seat♪
Dialogue: 0,1:55:37.78,1:55:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs14\i1}♪我的自行车后座♪\N{\rEng\fs10\i1}♪Of a bicycle built for two♪
Dialogue: 0,1:55:44.37,1:55:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日安  先生们\NGood day, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:50.59,1:55:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是预先录制的简报\NThis is a prerecorded briefing...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:53.63,1:55:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在你们出发前就已录好\Nmade prior to your departure...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:57.10,1:56:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出于最高级别的安全考虑\Nand which, for security reasons of the highest importance...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:02.27,1:56:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该信息在任务执行期间\Nhas been known onboard during the mission...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:05.94,1:56:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仅告知了飞船上的HAL 9000计算机\Nonly by your HAL 9000 computer.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:11.86,1:56:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord0\shad0\fs10\pos(190,219)\b1}海伍德·弗洛伊德博士\N国家航天委员会
Dialogue: 0,1:56:12.11,1:56:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在你们已进入木星空间\NNow that you are in Jupiter's space...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:15.20,1:56:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全体航天员也已苏醒\Nand the entire crew is revived...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:17.91,1:56:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以告诉你们了\Nit can be told to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:22.45,1:56:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,18个月前\NEighteen months ago...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:25.79,1:56:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地球之外存在智慧生命的首个证据\Nthe first evidence of intelligent life off the Earth...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:30.21,1:56:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被发现\N...was discovered.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:33.51,1:56:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该证据被掩埋在月球表面以下40英尺处\NIt was buried 40 feet below the lunar surface...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:37.22,1:56:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,靠近第谷月坑\Nnear the crater Tycho.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:42.35,1:56:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了对木星发出\NExcept for a single, very powerful...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:45.64,1:56:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,单束强劲的射电辐射\Nradio emission aimed at Jupiter...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:50.82,1:56:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这块有400万年历史的黑色巨石\Nthe 4-million-year-old black monolith
Dialogue: 0,1:56:53.19,1:56:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直保持绝对静默\Nhas remained completely inert...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:57.74,1:57:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其起源和用途\Nits origin and purpose...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:01.20,1:57:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,依然是个彻头彻尾的谜\N...still a total mystery.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:06.45,1:57:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(192,40)\b1\shad0\bord0\fs25\fax0\fad(0,0)\c&HFFFFEE&}木星{\fs19} \N\N及宇宙尽头之外


